The evidence with the title 'Obama, Romney don't tell whole truth in debate - NY Daily News ' says Oct 4, 2012  ... Obama's february budget offered proposals that would cut deficits over the coming decade by $2 trillion instead of $4 trillion.  ... New York Daily News  ... A Washington research group, says that would reduce federal tax revenues by $465 billion in 2015, which would add up to about $5 trillion over 10 years. 
